findings.title: Dividend tracker may be changed
findings.description: The logic of setBalance and other functions could be different and not audited if the dividend tracker is changed.

findings.title: Owner can grant access to transfer before trading is enabled
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to grant access to transfer before trading is enabled, which may lead to unauthorized transactions.

findings.title: Owner can change trading enabled timestamp
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the trading enabled timestamp.

findings.title: Owner can change dividend tracker address
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to change the dividend tracker address which could lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner can change Pancake router address
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the Pancake router address, which could lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner Privilege: Modification of automatedMarketMakerPairs Array
findings.description: The owner has the ability to exclude and include addresses in the automatedMarketMakerPairs array, which can lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: Owner can exclude from the fees
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to exclude addresses from fees, which may lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner can change liquidity wallet address
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the liquidity wallet address, which could lead to unauthorized access or manipulation of funds.

findings.title: Owner can change gas for processing
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify gas for processing which could lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: Owner can update claimWait value
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to update the claimWait value which could potentially lead to unintended consequences.
